      <title>加拿大因诉讼和政治不确定性推迟资本利得税改革至 2026 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/canada-delays-capital-gains-tax-change-to-2026-amid-lawsuits-politics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于该措施面临法律挑战且遭到主要政界人士的否认，加拿大将把资本利得纳入税率的提高推迟到2026年1月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/canada-delays-capital-gains-tax-change-to-2026-amid-lawsuits-politics</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 15:58:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼承诺废除加拿大碳税，该税似乎已死</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/canada-carbon-tax-appears-dead-after-carney-pledges-to-scrap-it</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大针对消费燃料征收的国家碳税可能即将进入最后几周，此前接替总理贾斯汀·特鲁多担任自由党领袖的两位主要候选人均承诺废除该税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/canada-carbon-tax-appears-dead-after-carney-pledges-to-scrap-it</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 15:25:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥警告特朗普 25% 关税将是一个“战略错误”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/mexico-warns-trump-25-tariffs-would-be-a-strategic-mistake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥政府告诉唐纳德·特朗普，对其产品征收 25% 关税的计划将是一个错误，会增加美国消费者的成本。而就在前一天，特朗普于周六再次承诺将对墨西哥产品征收 25% 的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/mexico-warns-trump-25-tariffs-would-be-a-strategic-mistake</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 15:21:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿斯利康因英国资金问题取消疫苗中心投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/astrazeneca-calls-off-vaccine-hub-investment-over-uk-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在与英国新工党政府就该疫苗生产厂的政府资助金额问题发生长期争论后，阿斯利康公司放弃了向英国一家疫苗生产厂投资 4.5 亿英镑（5.58 亿美元）的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/astrazeneca-calls-off-vaccine-hub-investment-over-uk-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:47:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利称委内瑞拉下令关闭领事馆，因争端加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/chile-says-venezuela-orders-consulates-to-close-as-spat-worsens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利政府表示，委内瑞拉以“中断外交关系”为由下令关闭其驻智利领事馆，这标志着两个南美国家之间的敌对状态升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/chile-says-venezuela-orders-consulates-to-close-as-spat-worsens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:40:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英伟达首席执行官黄仁勋将于周五在白宫会见特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/nvidia-ceo-huang-to-meet-trump-at-white-house-on-friday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，总统唐纳德·特朗普将于周五在白宫会见英伟达公司首席执行官黄仁勋。几天前，DeepSeek 推出的中国新人工智能模型引发了科技行业领袖的担忧，并导致美国股市暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/nvidia-ceo-huang-to-meet-trump-at-white-house-on-friday</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:28:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
